
Generate vertices
size = x * y
i = (x, y, 0)

Generate Indices

find indices
top left = y * width + x
top right = topleft + 1
bottom left = topleft + width
bottom right = bottom left + 1

create triangles
bottom left, top left, top right
bottom left, top right, bottom right

// triangle 1
indices[i] = vertices[bottom_left]
indices[i+1] = vertices[top_left]
indices[i+2] = vertices[top_right]
// triangle 2
indices[i +3] = vertices[..]

Load in game,
load geometry into buffer, return entity for offsets